<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Dark_Night_of_the_Soul&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>May, Gerald G. (2004). <i>The Dark Night of the Soul: A Psychiatrist Explores the Connection Between Darkness and Spiritual Growth</i>. HarperSanFrancisco. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0060554231" class="internal">ISBN 0-06-055423-1</a>.</li>
<li>McKee, Kaye P. (2006). <a href="http://search.barnesandnoble.com/When-God-Walks-Away/Kaye-McKee/e/9780824523800/?itm=2" class="external text" title="http://search.barnesandnoble.com/When-God-Walks-Away/Kaye-McKee/e/9780824523800/?itm=2" rel="nofollow">"When God Walks Away: A Companion to the Dark Night of the Soul."</a> Crossroad Publishing Company. ISBN-13: 9780824523800</li>
</ul>
